00:28:06,640 --> 00:28:07,640
Kuantarkan kalian.

408
00:28:18,839 --> 00:28:19,928
Ayo.

409
00:28:43,480 --> 00:28:44,536
Satu, dua, tiga.

410
00:28:47,759 --> 00:28:51,119
